tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE errors (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    error_message TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE RobotOperationalData (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  temperature FLOAT,
  battery_level FLOAT,
  robot_id INT,
  operation_mode TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE logs (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
error_message VARCHAR,
error_code INT,
timestamp TIMESTAMP)
